Waitrose Plans Franchise Expansion Overseas, Independent Says

-- B y   B e n   F a r e y
-- 
2011-02-20T11:31:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-20/waitrose-plans-franchise-expansion-overseas-independent-says.html
Waitrose, the U.K. supermarket brand
owned by  John Lewis Partnership Plc , is planning an overseas
franchise expansion with stores in  South Africa ,  Australia  and
the  Far East , the  Independent on Sunday  reported.  Waitrose plans to open 10 supermarkets and as many as 30  convenience stores  this year and has begun talks with potential
franchise partners, the newspaper reported, citing Nigel Keen,
head of development at the company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Farey in London  bfarey@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
